'From Squeak2.8alpha of 12 January 2000 [latest update: #1940] on 22 March 2000 at 4:07:30 pm'!"Change Set:		FasterWorldMenuDate:			22 March 2000Author:			Dan IngallsMakes 'self world project' run incomparably faster most of the time."!!Project class methodsFor: 'utilities' stamp: 'di 3/22/2000 16:07'!ofWorld: aPasteUpMorph	"Find the project of a world."	"Usually it is the current project"	self current world == aPasteUpMorph ifTrue: [^ self current].	"Inefficient enumeration if it is not..."	^ self allSubInstances		detect:		[:pr | pr world isInMemory 			ifTrue: [pr world == aPasteUpMorph]			ifFalse: [false]]		ifNone: [nil]! !